<div class="answer-head">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730"
class="zm-item-link-avatar"
href="/people/kaiserwang730">
<img src="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg"
class="zm-list-avatar"
data-source="//pic1.zhimg.com/21cb65b48_s.jpg" />
</a>



<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="44">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$guo-jun-68-87" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/guo-jun-68-87" class="zg-link" title="郭君">郭君</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yao-qing-shu" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yao-qing-shu" class="zg-link" title="坠吼是窝">坠吼是窝</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-dan-87-7" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-dan-87-7" class="zg-link" title="Liu Dan">Liu Dan</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2065494" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">侍郎于公，得子名曰冠胤。及冠胤九岁，于公以文字狱见诛，家私尽皆罚没。冠胤仅以父一官印得免，亡山中，自习武艺。<br><br>逾十年，有大成，更得潜行之术。冠胤隐于宫门外，虽有禁卫鱼贯而出竟不得见，江湖传作“鱼贯隐”。冠胤携父官印，潜宫中，决计刺驾报父仇。入后宫，见帝共后妃行鱼水之事，胤壮年，未尝见牝户，血气乱则显形。上大怒：“汝欲观阴耶？”侍卫乃入，斫其首。<br><br>事泄，皆云“于冠胤，与官印，鱼贯隐，欲观阴”。<br>乡人感其孝，制断头玉观音，是有此宝。


</div>

</div>
